Featured Products






Increase Productivity with Better Quality and More Efficient Lighting.
Eco Low-Profile High Bays

                     Our Eco Low-Profile High Bays bring increased energy efficiency to the workspace, improving the return on your lighting investment. 
                

                    View Solutions
                







The High Efficiency LED Lighting Solution for Indoor High Bay Applications.
Eco SpunBay

                    Specifically designed to provide superior uniformity and low-glare illumination for high visibility, these advanced LED high bays are 50% more efficient than traditional lighting, and with 0-10V dimming they can provide even higher energy savings.
                

                    View Solutions
                







Retrofit the Lighting in Your Facility with our Buy American Act (BAA) Compliant Solutions.
T8 BAA LED Tubes

                    High efficiency Buy American Act (BAA) compliant lighting retrofit solutions that can be installed into any new or existing fixture designed for similar fluorescent lamps and can reduce lighting energy use by as much as 60%.
                

                    View Solutions
                







Increase Visibility with Brighter, More Efficient Lighting.
Eco Linear High Bays

                    Designed for easy mounting to replace existing fluorescent or MH high bays, these strong, lightweight, fully-assembled fixtures provide superior uniformity for high visibility. The efficiency of Eco Linear High Bays reduces energy consumption by 50% over existing fluorescent fixtures, increasing the return on your lighting investment.
                

                    View Solutions
                



























