Company Summary
Revolution Technologies Inc. designs, manufacture, market and sells commercial grade, LED replacement light bulbs and LED-based signage, channel letter and contour lighting products. It operates in two segments: LED replacement lamps and LED signage and lighting strips. Revolution Technologies Inc., formerly known as Nexxus Lighting, Inc., is based in Aurora, Canada.   





 



 












